WEBVTT

01:29:06.048 --> 01:29:07.756
earned hundreds of crores.

01:29:08.464 --> 01:29:09.714
It was all for you.

01:29:11.006 --> 01:29:13.464
You've made me ashamed to even call you my son.

01:29:13.798 --> 01:29:17.339
I'm warning you...
stop all these illegal activities.

01:29:18.548 --> 01:29:20.256
Your time is up, Dad.

01:29:20.964 --> 01:29:22.214
shut up and step aside.

01:29:22.881 --> 01:29:24.214
Hey... are you threatening me?

01:29:24.464 --> 01:29:25.923
You still don't know me.

01:29:27.048 --> 01:29:30.464
My word is final... I won't give you even a penny.
